Contrat d'achat/vente d'equity FlexUp:
- Fred vend à Fabrizio de l'equity et des parts qu'il détient dans FlexUp
- L'equity est acheté à sa valeur nominale (1 € cash payé = 1 € d'equity transféré)
- Pour chaque 1 € cash payé / equity transféré, Fred cède à Fabrizio un nombre de part équivalent, à la valeur de la part à la date de payement, et aux taux de risque de l'equity vendu

Exemple:
- 5000 € payé = 5000 € d'equity transféré
- s'il s'agit d'equity simple, cela fait 100% de facteur de risque, 5000 € de risque
- si le prix de la part est de 200 €/part, cela fait donc 25 parts.

principal_period.principal_due_date_detailed_description: Payment is due at beginning of the month, even if the invoice has not been provided. This is only possible for recurring orders, where delivery occurs over the monthly period, and with a fixed amount (such as rent, subscription, retainers, salary, etc.)

Payment is due at the end of the month, even if the invoice has not been provided.
This is only possible for:
• recurring orders, where delivery occurs over the monthly period, and with a fixed amount (such as rent, subscription, retainers, salary, etc.)
• or for orders where the client calculates the amount due (such as a company calculating the the payroll for employees)

principal_period.principal_period_description: Payment is due at the end of the next month following delivery, provided invoice is received at least 15 days before the end of the next month
principal_period.principal_due_date_detailed_description:
• Payment is due at the end of the first month X in which 2 conditions are met (i) delivery was finished before the beginning of month X and (ii) invoice was received at least 15 days before the end of month X.
• If supplier sends invoice for month N at least 15 days before the end of month N+1, then payment will be due at the end of month N+1.
• If supplier sends invoice later on, then payment is due at the end of the month Y in which the invoice was received, if received at least 15 days before the end of month Y, otherwise at the end of month Y+1
